                        <interp inst="t18500916-name-600" type="given" value="FRANCIS"></interp>FRANCIS IRELAND</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, L</hi> 119). I took the prisoner—I asked what he was at there—he said he thought a person named Davis, a boot and shoemaker, lived there. <hi rend="smallCaps">
